x4freetext: (n,7Be) data measured in the same experimental work
Stacked foils, each target set consisted of a target
foil, with corresponding catcher foils, sandwiched
between Al and Cu monitor ( and catcher) foils.
The proton energy at the target locations was
determined from measured cross section ratios of the
monitor reactions in each target set.
Irradiated for 4 h with 100 nA at TSL
Irradiated for 12 h with 0.5 to 2 uA at KFA
